2026-05-10T21:32:19.2045814Z 12    <!--
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2046169Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2046501Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2047222Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2047567Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2047959Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
