2026-05-10T21:32:19.2050870Z 21    <!--
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2051220Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2051395Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2051716Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2052162Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2052477Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2052772Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2053237Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2053545Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2053847Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2054109Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-10T21:32:19.2054257Z 32    -->
